0.276(9) D and mu(upsilon' = 5) = 0.261(7) D. An RKR analysis allowed the first
two moments of the dipole moment function to be derived. Quantum beats were observed
for the f-parity Lambda-doublets and the partial resolution of the hyperfine structure
allowed the hyperfine energy level ordering to be determined. Accurate molecular
