and hyperfine coupling spectroscopic constants. Absolute intensities have also
been obtained and the vibrational dipole moment of the 1 ← O subbands, as well
as the Herman-Wallis coefficients, were determined through an analysis of these
new intensities and of those reported by M. N. Spencer, C. Chakerian, Jr., L. P.
Giver, and L. R. Brown (J. Mol. Spectrosc.165, 506-524, 1994). These constants
and the ones reported for the 2 ← 1 allowed subbands and the 1 ← 0 forbidden
